title: How to NOT Live with Regrets
itunes:title: How to NOT Live with Regrets
description:
My biggest fear is to get to the end of my life and wish that I would've done more with my time on Earth.

In this episode, I am going to teach you how to live a life free from regrets. What's most important is to make sure that when you get to the end of your life, you feel pride for what you did and how you lived.

Follow me on Instagram @RobDialJr https://instagram.com/robdialjr
